EDUCATIONAL AND ETHICAL USE DISCLAIMER

This software is provided for EDUCATIONAL PURPOSES ONLY and is intended to be 
used for:

1. Learning cybersecurity concepts and techniques
2. Authorized security testing and penetration testing
3. Security research on systems you own or have explicit permission to test
4. Academic research and coursework in cybersecurity

PROHIBITED USES:

1. Unauthorized access to computer systems or networks
2. Any illegal activities or malicious use
3. Violation of terms of service of any online platform
4. Any activity that violates local, state, national, or international laws

LEGAL RESPONSIBILITY:

Users of this software are solely responsible for ensuring their use complies 
with all applicable laws and regulations. The author(s) and contributors shall 
not be held liable for any misuse, damages, or legal consequences resulting 
from the use of this software.

ACKNOWLEDGMENT:

By using this software, you acknowledge that you understand and agree to use 
it only for lawful and ethical purposes. You also acknowledge that 
cybersecurity tools can be powerful and must be used responsibly.

EDUCATIONAL CONTEXT:

This software was developed as part of cybersecurity education at the Egyptian 
Chinese University. It is intended to help students and professionals learn 
about information gathering, network analysis, and security assessment 
techniques in a controlled and legal environment.

REPORTING MISUSE:

If you become aware of any misuse of this software, please report it to the 
appropriate authorities and contact the author.

